Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:02.24,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}eiga mitai ni aoi natsu no umi wo mite
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.53,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}tooi tokoro de ibasho wo shiri
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:06.04,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}ima to ima wo kasaneteku, firumu no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:07.54,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}nankai mo torinaoshi da
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:10.54,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}iroaseru yori, irodoru yori, kimi no iru keshiki ga koi na
