Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:13.54,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}sou omottan da, tada mayoi naku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:14.96,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}shinjitemo ii ka to kikareta
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.55,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}tatta sore dake no toi da
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:18.09,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}kangaeterun da, donna toki mo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:19.42,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}ano koe ga tsukimatoi nagara
