Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:22.34,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}sou ka, kono kimochi ga koi da
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:37.32,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}sennen mae no tomoshibi ni nobashita nipon no yubi ga
